=== OVERVIEW === 

This is purely in alpha status, right now it does the following:

 * Generate a gemspec purely from the information availabe in the Maven project
 * Generate a gem from a gemspec
 * Provides packaging type "gem" with it's own default lifecycle bindings.

In the short-term, it also intends to provide the following (incomplete):

 * Resolution of gem artifacts from actual gem repositories, via Maven

Long-term goals will be listed here shortly...

=== INSTALLATION ===

Right now, this plugin requires Maven 2.2.1 or newer.

To build with Maven and install to your local repository, simply run:

      mvn install


=== USAGE ===

To use this plugin, add the following to your plugins section in your pom.xml:

      <plugin>
        <groupId>com.ankhcraft.maven.plugins</groupId>
        <artifactId>maven-gem-plugin</artifactId>
        <extensions>true</extensions>
        <version>0.1</version>
      </plugin>


